----------------------------------------------------
INSTALLATION HOWTO:
1. Install below packages for python environment under windows(7):
    1>python-2.7.3.msi(mandatory)
    2>PIL-1.1.7.win32-py2.7.exe(mandatory)
    3>numpy-1.6.2-win32-superpack-python2.7.exe(mandatory)
    4>opencv2.4.2.exe (optional)
    5>matplotlib-1.2.0rc3.win32-py2.7 (optional, only used when debug)
    Notes: 32bit version shold be used for above packages, as no 64bit opencv python lib was abailable temporarily.

2. If step 1.4 is skipped, pls copy the existing "cv2.pyd" to your python2.7 site-packages folder
"C:\Python27\Lib\site-packages\".

3. Add "C:\Python27" into windows environment variable "Path".

4. Enjoy it.

----------------------------------------------------
USAGE HOWTO:
1. run-time directories hierarchy:
    working directory: .../workdir/
    input:
        source image directory: .../workdir/src/
        default config file: .../scriptdir/default_config_file.txt
        input config file: .../workdir/input_config_file.txt
    output:
        run-time log file: .../workingdir/log.txt
        processed image directory: .../workdir/dst/
        output data file directory: .../workdir/


